# This is a split the bill calculator it will help you to split the blll among uour friends with tipppp!!!!!!
Bill = float(input("Please enter the bill:\n₹"))
Tip = float(input("Please enter the percent of tip you want to pay\n"))
No_of_people = int(input("Please enter how many people are you:\n"))
Total_Bill = (Bill+(Tip/100*Bill)) / No_of_people

# Now it will calculate the money each person has to pay
print(f"Each people has to pay ₹{round(Total_Bill,2)}")
